{
  "stem": "9963.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When we come to Gleiwitz, to Gleiwitz II, we stayed over there for three days.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they put us on the wagons, on open wagons what they took us to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The train was traveling, was standing more than traveling, because there was such a traffic that we were just on the train and on the side standing.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the meantime, other trains are coming up and down, up and down.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Several hundred-- several hundred people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What this-- several were wagons, you know-- I couldn't imagine how many people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In that train, was only men, because only the men-- I don't know what's happened to the woman, but the way in Buna Auschwitz were women too, but I don't know what's happened to them, where they went.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the train.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have anything to eat for days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nothing to drink.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The only thing what we've got is, it was open wagons-- if the snow fall at night, what we could get the snow together a little bit and take and wet our mouths from-- with the snow.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that's the only thing we got for like 10 days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You had over there the corners, what you did, what you did it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a very unsanitary thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- if somebody needed number two, it was little windows, you know, what we would pick them up and they stick out the behind.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, number one we went inside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But number two, we picked them up and they stick out the behind and let it go.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you know, the funny thing is, what is not so funny, but many times, the SS were standing on every wagon.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If the-- if the wind was in the right direction-- [LAUGHS] You know?",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
